                  <handDesc>
                     
                     <handNote xml:id="h1" script="Ethiopic">
                        <seg type="script">Careful.</seg>
                        <seg type="ink">Black, vivid red.</seg>
                        <date>Second half of the 19th century.</date>
                        <list type="abbreviations">
                           <item>ይካ፡ for ይብል፡ ካህን፡</item>
                           <item>ይዲ፡ for ይብል፡ ዲያቆን፡</item>
                        </list>
                        <seg type="rubrication">Nomina sacra; incipit of Texts I-II; directives to
                           the ministers and their abbreviations; titles of books to be read;
                           initial word of payers to be read; elements of the punctuation signs;
                           elements of Ethiopic numerals. 
 On the incipit page of Text I (fols.
                           3r) and on fol. 32rb, a few lines are rubricated (alternating with black
                           lines).</seg>
                     </handNote>
                  </handDesc>
                  <decoDesc>

                     <decoNote type="frame" xml:id="d1">
                        <locus target="#37rb">37rb</locus>: simple ornamental band; geometric
                        motifs.</decoNote>
                  </decoDesc>
                  <additions>
                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="e1">
                           <desc type="findingAid">- Daily readings are indicated by the names of the
                              days of the week written in frames in the upper margin: ዘሰኑይ: <locus target="#3r">fol. 3r</locus>. ዘሠሉስ: <locus target="#7v">fol.
                                 7v</locus>. ዘረቡዕ: <locus target="#11v">fol. 11v</locus>. ዘሐሙስ:
                                 <locus target="#16r">fol. 16r</locus>. ዘዓርብ: <locus target="#21v">fol. 21v</locus>. ዘቀዳም: <locus target="#27r">fol. 27r</locus>.
                              ዘእኁድ: <locus target="#32r">fol. 32r</locus>.</desc>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e3">
                           <desc>- Name of the church crudely written in blue pen: <locus target="#1r">fol.  1r</locus>. - Names of individuals crudely written in blue pen: <locus target="#39r">fol.  39r</locus>. - Doodles: <locus target="#1r">fol.  1r</locus>. - Space for a rubricated name left unfilled: <locus target="#9r">fol.  9r</locus>.</desc>
                        </item>
                     </list>
                  </additions>
